n**Dataset Overview:**\n- **Source:** UCI Superconductivity Database + 3DSC Materials Project\n- **Total Superconductors:** 21,263 materials with Tc > 0K\n- **Features Used:** 10 elemental statistics (atomic mass, radius, valence, etc.)\n- **PCA Reduction:** 81 features → 2D space (retains 73.55% variance)\n\n**Composition Families:**\n- **3 Major Clusters** identified via DBSCAN\n- Cluster -1: Outlier/noise points\n- Cluster 0, 1: Primary composition families\n\n**High-Tc Materials:**\n- Tc > 50K: 5,872 materials (28%)\n- Tc > 100K: 1,423 materials (7%)\n- Max Tc: 185K\n\n**Under-Explored Regions:**\n- 34 sparse zones identified in full dataset\n- 5 sparse zones in fast sample\n- Located adjacent to high-Tc clusters = research opportunities\n\n---\n\n### 8. RECENT GIT HISTORY\n\nRecent commits show active development on rendering stability:\n\n```\n3828912 Hybrid version: full UI with simple reliable rendering\ne55cb9b Restore full UI with fast data - all features + working visualization\n65e9d5f Minimal working version - guaranteed to render visualization\n178c86e Use working version (78ec016) with fast data - CDN libs for guaranteed compatibility\n17bcb02 Add debug page to test Three.js loading\n```\n\n**Pattern:** Iterating between full-featured and minimal/reliable versions, using CDN libraries for broad compatibility.\n\n---\n\n### 9. SUPPORTING DOCUMENTATION\n\n- **README.md:** Full project overview, motivation, tech stack\n- **FOR_PERIODIC_LABS.md:** Pitch document explaining relevance to Periodic Labs' mission\n- **SUMMARY.md:** Concise summary\n- **DEPLOY.md:** Deployment instructions\n- **EMAIL_DRAFT.md:** Email template for outreach\n\n---\n\n### 10. LIBRARY BUNDLING\n\nLocal copies in `/Users/03-mac-alpha/.openclaw/workspace/supersearch/docs/lib/`:\n- **three.min.js** (589 KB) - Complete Three.js library\n- Post-processing modules: EffectComposer, RenderPass, UnrealBloomPass\n- Controls: OrbitControls\n- Geometry: ConvexGeometry\n\n**Fallback Strategy:*